    candidateQuadrangles.maxBy(quad ⇒ {
      val bounds = new Rectangle2D_F32()
      UtilPolygons2D_F32.bounding(quad, bounds)
      val area = quad.area()
      val squareness = area / bounds.area()
      assert(squareness >= 0 && squareness <= 1.01)
      area * Math.pow(squareness, 2)
    })
